./install <openrc> <tag> <ssh_key> #excluding the openrc file the other two are just name strings.
./operate <openrc> <tag> <ssh_key> 
./cleanup <openrc> <tag> <ssh_key>

RULES:
Before running Operate or Cleanup, you must run install as it will create the necessary resources (venv) and generate the necessary files.

Requirements:
python3 # The script will install required stuff. 
apt 
bash 